Do this little audit when you leave someone — ask yourself, 
do you leave a filled cup, ignited from the conversation and energy exchange? Or do you leave depleted, maybe an empty cup from the energy drained?

Be mindful of this — the energy vampires VS. the ppl who give you life. 💡💛✨

Life is short. Invest time and stick around the people who uplift you, are positive in nature, want you to win & supper you on your journey. 

This makes all the difference. 🙏🏼 x
